Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:23.87,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5} Se um vidente disesse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:27.20,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}que nossa compatibilidade
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.46,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5} não é lá essas coisas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:34.00,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}ele seria um impostor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:37.50,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Não, não pode, não se deixe enganar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:41.47,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Quem decide o destino sou eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:43.30,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Isso mesmo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:48.26,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}este é o amor verdadeiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:54.10,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}É o tipo de coisa que, após morrermos
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:58.48,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}será exibida em um museu de arte.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:04.95,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Por isso, me deixe sempre em primeiro lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:08.54,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Me ame com todo carinho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:14.67,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}até que estas mãos que seguramos se fundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:18.55,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Vamos ficar sempre nessa vibe boa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:21.97,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Se formos nós dois, será moleza.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:28.18,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Fique ao meu lado, mesmo que estejamos "chapados" de amor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:31.02,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Por favor.
